name: MIKU IS POSSESSED
description:
Miku is feeling strange lately... she went to the doctor, but he was no help. 

She can feel her sanity slowly crumbling, and her mind unraveling day by day...

A voice whispers to her as she dreams... a cruel, dark, ancient voice.

When she wakes up she can never quite remember what the voice said...

But she knows it wasn't something good.
